    • isCritical

      public boolean isCritical()
      Shows this damage instance was critical. The damage instance can be critical if the attacking player met the respective conditions. Furthermore arrows may also cause a critical damage event if the arrow AbstractArrow.isCritical().
      Returns:
      if the hit was critical.
